titles.title: Directing the Secretary of the Senate to make a technical correction in the enrollment of S. 1438.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

vote.text: Received in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Unanimous Consent.

action.text: Message on Senate action sent to the House.

bill.summary: 12/13/2001--Passed Senate without amendment. Directs the Secretary of the Senate to make specified corrections in the enrollment of S. 1438 (FY 2002 Department of Defense funding authorization).
